There are electric heavy stackers, manual heavy stackers, and semi-electric heavy stackers available in the market.

4. What are the key applications of heavy stackers?
Heavy stackers are used for stacking pallets, loading and unloading trucks, and transporting heavy materials in warehouses and distribution centers.

